  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Bassin's Black Bass is a fishing game in which players aim to become a professional fisherman. It is part of Starfish's Black Bass fishing game series and their second title on the SNES. Originally titled Super Black Bass 2, the game was renamed for the US release and endorsed by the professional fishing champion Hank Parker. The object of the game is for the player to become a professional fisherman and can travel by themselves or along with Hank.",
